<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>My Portfolio</title>

<style>
html, body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: lightblue;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
}

body {
    text-align: center;
    overflow-y: auto;
}

.top-section {
    padding: 20px 0;
}

.introduce-button {
    height: 50px;
    font-size: 25px;
    font-weight: bold;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background-color: lightyellow;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(50px);
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
}

.animation-link {
    display: inline-block;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: #9400D3;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(190,0,255,0.7);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(-50px);
    animation: slideDown 2s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.5s;
    margin-top: 10px;
}

@keyframes fadeUp {
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

@keyframes slideDown {
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

.center-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 40px;
}

.kielpicture {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 20px 0;
}

.picturekiel {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.7s;
}

.kiel-name {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.8s;
}

.moreaboutme {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 10px auto 20px auto;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 1.2s;
}

.skills {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 1.5s;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.skills ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
}

.skills a {
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: #9400D3;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(190,0,255,0.7);
}

.kiel-skills {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    margin-top: 10px;
}

.skills-achievement {
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 10px auto 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.5;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="top-section">
    <button class="introduce-button">Welcome To My Portfolio</button><br>
    <a href="#" class="animation-link">ABOUT ME</a>
</div>

<div class="center-section">
    <h4 class="kiel-name">Hello, my name is Ezekiel Andrada Flores</h4>

    <div class="kielpicture">
        <img src="https://scontent.fmnl33-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-1/615817608_892084013360261_4209581895590661230_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_s200x200_tt6&_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=e99d92&_nc_eui2=AeECex0b-J-9vRXYLvpSN-_cCMoWBPnouTsIyhYE-ei5O1L_nQGRrvdmFEGtT2Ge7OYLhK6-VWpi27E-dSow4_Hn&_nc_ohc=b9MIfCNg3QYQ7kNvwGu_xYK&_nc_oc=Adn1nQqIdQ3q22kluN-QgsKNmCK5cfNK6tHOgPLEzdLsfHjH--frxa3C6Y7ycNFy0LQ&_nc_zt=24&_nc_ht=scontent.fmnl33-1.fna&_nc_gid=DWDupxnTvm2cI1NZ07FIyw&oh=00_AfvochgXUiPHiumHrAynElypTpjvZ0rcU9EAi1J20uvuPQ&oe=699E4E7B" alt="Kiel Face" class="picturekiel">
    </div>

    <p class="moreaboutme">
        I am 16 years old from San Pablo City, Laguna. I am a Grade 11 student at CMDI. 
        I want to take an IT course in college. In the future, I want to become a Web Developer 
        because it offers a high salary in the IT industry.
    </p>

    <div class="skills">
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#">SKILLS</a></li>
        </ul>
        <h3 class="kiel-skills">My Skills and Achievements</h3>
        <p class="skills-achievement">
            - Naka immortal nang solo<br>
            - Yearner Final Boss<br>
            - Dumudurog nang lima<br>
            - Palo mag Fredrinn at Yss
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
